Mentor Academy was created by Vinnie Fisher, author of "Beyond Your Shadow: Legacy Through Multiplication" and founder of multiple successful businesses.
After building and selling companies worth millions, Vinnie discovered his true calling—helping experienced professionals package their wisdom into thriving mentorship businesses. He developed the Multiplication Method to help others skip the years of trial and error he experienced.
Our team has collectively guided thousands of mentees and built successful mentoring practices across diverse industries. We've distilled everything we've learned into a comprehensive system that gives you a dramatic head start in your mentor business journey.
